490
00:41:14,000 --> 00:41:17,019
You'll lose your arms before you finish copying ten pages.

491
00:41:17,640 --> 00:41:22,760
How can the Supreme Head of the Six Realms be this vicious?

492
00:41:24,000 --> 00:41:25,520
Yan Dan.

