497
00:41:38,459 --> 00:41:39,879
Can't you see it?

498
00:41:39,880 --> 00:41:43,399
His Supreme Majesty has found out that there is something going on between us.

499
00:41:43,399 --> 00:41:48,720
If it wasn't for my acting skills, we would have been sent to the Heavenly Gallows, awaiting our punishments!

500
00:41:59,760 --> 00:42:02,659
