501
00:42:02,659 --> 00:42:04,380
Looks like something is bothering you.

502
00:42:04,380 --> 00:42:07,280
Don't tell me His Supreme Majesty got it right.

503
00:42:07,280 --> 00:42:09,480
Did you not stay abstinent?

504
00:42:19,720 --> 00:42:21,320
Are you done yet?

505
00:42:22,620 --> 00:42:25,760
So you and Si Xuan...

506
00:42:28,180 --> 00:42:29,980
I killed her.

507
00:42:35,040 --> 00:42:36,860
You...

508
00:42:36,860 --> 00:42:38,560
Why?

509
00:42:43,600 --> 00:42:45,540
She didn't stay abstinent.

510
00:42:46,240 --> 00:42:50,400
I executed her at the Heavenly Gallows.

